Package: isochron
Title: tools for calculating and plotting isochrons
Description: isochron is a set of tools that calculate best fit lines
    to geochemical data for the construction and interpretation of isochrons.
    Two common methods of fitting the data are provided as well as functions to
    determine the age, uncertainty, and fit statistics from the measured data.
